<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="M.C3.A9moire_politique_:_Michel_Herbillon.2C_d.C3.A9put.C3.A9"><a href="/wiki/Memoire_politique" title="Memoire politique" class="mw-redirect">Mémoire politique</a>&#160;: Michel Herbillon, député</span></h2>
<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:MichelHerbillon.jpg" class="image" title="Michel Herbillon"><img alt="Michel Herbillon" src="/wiki/images/3/39/MichelHerbillon.jpg" width="150" height="192" /></a></div>
